text: Hanna Stanek-Lisowska (4 May 1938 – 14 December 2020) was a Polish actress."Hanna Stankówna" at filmpolski.pl She was born in Poznań, Poland. She was known for her roles in The Real End of the Great War, Lokis and The Third Part of the Night. Stankówna died on 14 December 2020 in Warsaw at the age of 82.Nie żyje aktorka Hanna Stankówna ==References== Category:1938 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish movie actors Category:Polish stage actors Category:Actors from Poznań
